<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../static/css/firstpage.css" />
        <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="../static/img/favicon.png" />
        <title>FALLACIES</title>
    </head>
    <body onload="loaded()">
        <div id="loader"><img src="../static/img/loading.gif" alt="Loading..." class="loading-gif"></div>
        <img src="../static/img/CSIDark(saturated).png" alt="CSI LOGO" class="csilogo" />
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <img src="../static/img/title.png" alt="LOGO" class="logo" />
                <h2 class="description">What if we told you everything you believe is a lie?</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="innercontainer">
                <img src="../static/img/eye-pyramid.png" alt="Eye pyramid" class="innercontainer__image innercontainer__image--pyramid">
                <div class="buttons">
                    <button class="innercontainer__button innercontainer__button--play">PLAY</button>
                    <button class="innercontainer__button innercontainer__button--leaderboard">LEADERBOARD</button>
                </div>
                <img src="../static/img/ufo.png" alt="Eye pyramid" class="innercontainer__image innercontainer__image--ufo">
            </div>
            <div class="rulescontainer">
                <h3 style="text-align: center;">The Official Rulebook for FALLACIES 2020</h3>
                <br>
                <p class="rules" style="text-align: justify;">
                    <h4>-Overall Objective</h4>
                    Players scour through the clues and try to uncover the mysteries behind these conspiracy theories.<br><br>
                    <h4>-Rules/How to play</h4>
                    > Log into your account at fallacies.csivit.com and you will be presented with a hint to start your hunt!<br>
                    > Enter your answer into the text box and if youâ€™re worthy enough, they'll let you through to the next question.<br>
                    > Alternatively, you can use our Telegram Bot <a href="https://t.me/CSI_Brobot" style="text-decoration: none; color: #f00;">@CSI_Brobot</a> to enter your response.<br>
                    > Solve as many questions as you can and be the best conspiracy theorist.<br>
                    > Please refrain from any form of malpractice to maintain the spirit of the game. CSI-VIT holds the right to disqualify any participant involved.<br><br>
                    <h4>-Scoring</h4>
                    Each conspiracy that you decipher will earn you a point on the leader board.
                </p>
            </div>
            <button class="btn-signout">Log Out</button>
        </div>
        <script>
        if(document.getElementById("loader")) document.querySelector(".container").style.display = 'none';
        function loaded() {
            document.getElementById("loader").style.display = "none";
            document.querySelector(".container").style.display = "flex";
        }
        document.querySelector('.innercontainer__button--play').addEventListener('click', () => {
            window.location.replace('/submissions');
        });
        document.querySelector('.innercontainer__button--leaderboard').addEventListener('click', () => {
            window.location.replace('/leaderboard');
        });
        </script>
    </body>
</html>
